# UFCIM API — endpoint tests (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP Client)
#
# Setup:
#   1. Copy .dev.vars.example → .dev.vars
#   2. Apply migration: npx wrangler d1 execute ufcim-db --local --file=migrations/0000_lazy_wallow.sql
#   3. Apply seed:      npx wrangler d1 execute ufcim-db --local --file=scripts/seed.sql
#   4. Start worker:    npx wrangler dev --env dev
#   5. Refresh tokens below if expired: node scripts/generate-test-token.mjs [role]
#
# Seed UUIDs:
#   student     00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
#   professor   00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
#   staff       00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003
#   maintenance 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004
#   space A101  00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000011
#   space B205  00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000012
#   space C301  00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000013
#   projector   00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000021

